{
  "stem": "7546.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I says, let me go and see the baby, my sister's baby, the young one, the boy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- again, I had to go through, and now my sister and brother gave me yellow star I should wear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to my sister whose husband was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a better apartment, because of him being a doctor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was sort sought after by the men that led the Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name was Chaim Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the doctors were sort of a privileged crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There weren't too many, but as many as there were, they were privileged.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she had a two-room apartment and a kitchen, and also a toilet in the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately a few months later, they closed it, because a Jew wasn't allowed this luxury, so she had to use an outhouse.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But since she had more room and she loved it if I should be with the baby, and I slept in the same room where my-- where my little nephew was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I lived with my sister and with my brother-in-law for two years in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Unfortunately, I'm jumping ahead of myself, but since I have to finish with my sister, what happened was that there was a very big factory in a town near Lodz called Zelow.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were about 8,000 or 9,000 people working in the factory, and they had no medical care.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the-- the head of the Jewish ghetto asked some doctors if they would volunteer to go to a different town where they get good lodging and good care, and we were all taken care of because he'll be the doctor for that factory.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
